title: Morning Joe 2/16/21
description: House Speaker Nancy Pelosi, D-Calif., is doubling down on calls for a 9/11-style commission on the Capitol attack, following the impeachment and acquittal of former President Donald Trump. The Morning Joe panel discusses.
